&t;p&t;The original compilation of species were observed during sampling from 1971 to 1976 and listed in: &t;/p&t;

&t;p&t;McKee, A., R. Nussbaum, and C. Maser.  1976.  A checklist of the Terrestrial Vertebrates of the H.J. Andrews Experimental Forest. Unpublished. &t;/p&t;

&t;p&t;More recently, species have been observed and documented in: &t;/p&t;

&t;p&t;Bury, R.B. and P.S. Corn.  1988.  Douglas-fir forests in the Oregon and Washington Cascades: Relation of the herpetofauna to stand age and moisture.  pp. 11-22 in Szaro, R.C., K.E. Severson, D.R. Patton (eds.), Management of Amphibians, Reptiles and small mammals in North America. GTR-RM-166, USDA Forest Service, Rocky Mountain Forest and Range Experiment Station, Ft. Collins, CO. &t;/p&t;

&t;p&t;Bury, R.B., P.S. Corn, and K.B. Aubry.  1991.  Regional patterns of terrestrial amphibian communities in Oregon and Washington.  pp. 341-350 in Ruggiero, L.F., K.B. Aubry, A.B. Carey, M.H. Huff (tech. eds.), Wildlife and Vegetation of Unmanaged Douglas-fir Forests. GTR-PNW-285, USDA Forest Service, PNW Research Station, Portland, OR. &t;/p&t;

&t;p&t;Bury, R.B., P.S. Corn, K.B. Aubry, F.F. Gilbert, and L.L.C. Jones. 1991. Aquatic amphibian communities in Oregon and Washington.  pp. 353-362 in Ruggiero, L.F., K.B. Aubry, A.B. Carey, M.H. Huff (tech. eds.), Wildlife and Vegetation of Unmanaged Douglas-fir Forests. GTR-PNW-285, USDA Forest Service, PNW Research Station, Portland, OR. &t;/p&t;

&t;p&t;Gilbert, F.F. and R. Allwine.  1991.  Terrestrial amphibian communities in the Oregon Cascade Range.  pp. 319-324 in Ruggiero, L.F., K.B. Aubry, A.B. Carey, M.H. Huff (tech. eds.), Wildlife and Vegetation of Unmanaged Douglas-fir Forests. GTR-PNW-285,   USDA Forest Service, PNW Research Station, Portland, OR.&t;/p&t;

&t;p&t;Nomenclature for the amphibians follows &t;br&t; 
Leonard, W.P., H.A. Brown, L.L.C. Jones, K.R. McAllister, and R.M. Storm.  1993.  Amphibians of Washington and Oregon. Seattle Audubon Society, Seattle, WA. 168 pp. &t;/p&t;

&t;p&t;Nomenclature for the reptiles follows&t;br&t; 
Nussbaum, R.A., E.D. Brodie, Jr., and R.M. Storm.  1983. Amphibians &mp; Reptiles of the Pacific Northwest. University of Idaho Press, Moscow, Idaho. 332 pp.&t;/p&t;
